codex
I found a concrete review issue: `_API_KEY=` masking only handles unquoted values, so a prompt or log line containing `OPENAI_API_KEY="plain-token"` or `FOO_API_KEY='plain-token'` can be written verbatim unless it also matches one of the generic key regexes or is already present in `os.environ`. I’m writing the requested YAML review now.
